{
  "page": "Garibald Shells",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Garibald Shells</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Garibald Shells</b> is a young <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garibald_Shells&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Garibald is serious and proper young man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garibald_Shells&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garibald_Shells&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Garibald is chosen to accompany Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> on her journey to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> to meet with <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>. While traveling on the ship the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Peregrine\" title=\"Peregrine\">Peregrine</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Joss_Hood\" title=\"Joss Hood\">Joss Hood</a> finds <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Sand\" title=\"Elia Sand\">Elia Sand</a> to be too precocious for his liking and states that someone should spank her. Elia both flirts and challenges him, saying that he must joust her first if he wishes to punish her. While Garibald claims that women should not joust, Elia claims that she is \"Lady Lance\". Arianne Martell sends her below deck to end the conversation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>On the <i>Peregrine</i> he played a game of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cyvasse\" title=\"Cyvasse\">cyvasse</a></i> with Princess Arianne and wins.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garibald_Shells&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-sample-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">The Winds of Winter, Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:MartellPartyToAegon\" title=\"Template:MartellPartyToAegon\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:MartellPartyToAegon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:MartellPartyToAegon (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:MartellPartyToAegon&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>'s party to meet <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Sand\" title=\"Elia Sand\">Elia Sand</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Garibald Shells</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jayne_Ladybright\" title=\"Jayne Ladybright\">Jayne Ladybright</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joss_Hood\" title=\"Joss Hood\">Joss Hood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nate\" title=\"Nate\">Nate</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403143456\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.246 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 705/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9422/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11925/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1909/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 819/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  233.647      1 -total\n 94.31%  220.362      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 93.48%  218.423      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.48%   26.819     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.63%   10.808      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.35%    7.827      1 Template:MartellPartyToAegon\n  3.13%    7.311      1 Template:N